title: Dr Scott prefered books - The Great Pyramid Decoded - E Raymond
description:
This is one of Dr Scott's choices of books on Pyramids he gave away freely. The images are the pages scanned at high enough res you can zoom in for the details, and the cover is included...

 A real plus to have on hand with or without Dr Scotts video on this book.

 Some of the pages were what he copied and sent out as Doc Notes.

 This is hard to find as nobody wants to sell or give away their copy of the book.

It has been out of print for many years.
